<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Y - Your Yearning Soul | JYOTI KUSH</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
            background: #777a7c;
            min-height: 100vh;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            position: relative;
            color: #f4f4f4;
        }

        /* Unique wave animation background */
        .wave-bg {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: 1;
            background: 
                radial-gradient(circle at 30% 70%, rgba(56, 239, 125, 0.15) 0%, transparent 60%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 70% 30%, rgba(17, 153, 142, 0.12) 0%, transparent 50%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 20% 20%, rgba(139, 69, 19, 0.08) 0%, transparent 40%);
            animation: waveFlow 15s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
        }

        @keyframes waveFlow {
            0% { transform: translateX(0%) rotateZ(0deg); opacity: 0.4; }
            100% { transform: translateX(-5%) rotateZ(2deg); opacity: 0.7; }
        }

        /* Floating particles with different shapes */
        .particle {
            position: absolute;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, rgba(56, 239, 125, 0.4), rgba(17, 153, 142, 0.3));
            animation: particleFloat 12s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        .particle:nth-child(1) { width: 8px; height: 8px; top: 20%; left: 10%; border-radius: 50%; animation-delay: 0s; }
        .particle:nth-child(2) { width: 12px; height: 12px; top: 60%; right: 20%; border-radius: 30%; animation-delay: 2s; transform: rotate(45deg); }
        .particle:nth-child(3) { width: 6px; height: 6px; bottom: 30%; left: 30%; border-radius: 50%; animation-delay: 4s; }
        .particle:nth-child(4) { width: 10px; height: 10px; top: 40%; right: 10%; animation-delay: 6s; }

        @keyframes particleFloat {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0px) rotate(0deg); opacity: 0.3; }
            25% { transform: translateY(-40px) rotate(90deg); opacity: 0.8; }
            50% { transform: translateY(-20px) rotate(180deg); opacity: 0.6; }
            75% { transform: translateY(-60px) rotate(270deg); opacity: 0.9; }
        }

        .container {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 10;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            padding: 2rem;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        /* Header with side-by-side layout */
        .header {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 2rem 0;
            animation: slideInLeft 1.8s ease-out;
        }

        .header-content {
            flex: 1;
        }

        .page-title {
            font-size: 3rem;
            color: #38ef7d;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            text-shadow: 3px 3px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .subtitle {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #11998e;
            font-style: italic;
            text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
        }

        .header-decoration {
            width: 200px;
            height: 200px;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, rgba(56, 239, 125, 0.2), rgba(17, 153, 142, 0.2));
            border-radius: 50%;
            position: relative;
            animation: decorationSpin 20s linear infinite;
        }

        .header-decoration::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 20px;
            left: 20px;
            right: 20px;
            bottom: 20px;
            border: 2px solid rgba(56, 239, 125, 0.4);
            border-radius: 50%;
            animation: decorationSpin 15s linear infinite reverse;
        }

        @keyframes decorationSpin {
            from { transform: rotate(0deg); }
            to { transform: rotate(360deg); }
        }

        /* Description with diagonal layout */
        .description {
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 3rem 0;
            animation: fadeInScale 2.2s ease-out 0.6s both;
        }

        .description-content {
            max-width: 900px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            /* backdrop-filter: blur(20px); */
            border: 1px solid rgba(56, 239, 125, 0.2);
            border-radius: 25px;
            padding: 4rem;
            box-shadow: 0 25px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            transform: skewY(-2deg);
        }

        /* Enhanced background letter Y */
        .description-content::before {
            content: 'Y';
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%) skewY(2deg);
            font-size: 28rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #38ef7d, #11998e, #2d1b69, #38ef7d);
            background-size: 400% 400%;
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            opacity: 0.15;
            z-index: 1;
            animation: gradientFlow 5s ease-in-out infinite, letterPulse 10s ease-in-out infinite;
            pointer-events: none;
            filter: drop-shadow(0 0 25px rgba(56, 239, 125, 0.4)) 
                    drop-shadow(0 0 50px rgba(17, 153, 142, 0.3))
                    drop-shadow(0 0 75px rgba(45, 27, 105, 0.2));
        }

        @keyframes gradientFlow {
            0%, 100% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
            50% { background-position: 100% 50%; }
        }

        @keyframes letterPulse {
            0%, 100% { transform: translate(-50%, -50%) skewY(2deg) scale(1); }
            25% { transform: translate(-50%, -50%) skewY(2deg) scale(1.03) rotate(1deg); }
            50% { transform: translate(-50%, -50%) skewY(2deg) scale(0.97) rotate(-0.5deg); }
            75% { transform: translate(-50%, -50%) skewY(2deg) scale(1.01) rotate(0.5deg); }
        }

        .description-text {
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            line-height: 1.9;
            color:white;
            text-align: justify;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
            transform: skewY(2deg);
        }

        .highlight {
            color: #38ef7d;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(56, 239, 125, 0.5);
        }

        /* Hexagonal image grid */
        .image-grid {
            padding: 3rem 0;
            animation: slideInUp 2.5s ease-out 1.2s both;
        }

        .grid-container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 3rem;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

      .image-card {
  position: relative;
  width: 250px;
  height: 250px;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #38ef7d 0%, #11998e 50%, #2d1b69 100%);
  border-radius: 20px;
  overflow: hidden;
  transition: all 0.5s ease;
  cursor: pointer;
  box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
}


        .image-card:hover {
            transform: scale(1.1) rotate(5deg);
            box-shadow: 0 30px 60px rgba(56, 239, 125, 0.4);
        }

       .image-card::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  right: 0;
  bottom: 0;
  background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
  z-index: 1;
  transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
  opacity: 0;
}
.image-card:hover::before {
  opacity: 0.2;
}


        .image-card:hover::before {
            opacity: 0.3;
        }

       .image-content {
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  right: 0;
  bottom: 0;
  z-index: 2;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  justify-content: flex-end;
  padding: 1rem;
}


      .square-image {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  object-fit: cover;
  object-position: center;
  display: block;
  transition: transform 0.5s ease;
}
.image-card:hover .square-image {
  transform: scale(1.05);
}


        .image-card:hover .hexagon-image {
            transform: scale(1.1);
        }

        /* Navigation with different position */
        .navigation {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 2rem;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            z-index: 100;
        }

        .nav-btn {
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #38ef7d, #11998e);
            border: none;
            border-radius: 50px;
            padding: 1.2rem 2.5rem;
            color: white;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(56, 239, 125, 0.4);
            transition: all 0.4s ease;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .nav-btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(56, 239, 125, 0.6);
        }

        /* Responsive Design */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .header { flex-direction: column; text-align: center; gap: 2rem; }
            .header-decoration { width: 150px; height: 150px; }
            .page-title { font-size: 2.5rem; }
            .description-content { padding: 2.5rem; margin: 0 1rem; transform: skewY(0deg); }
            .description-content::before { font-size: 18rem; transform: translate(-50%, -50%); }
            .description-text { font-size: 1.2rem; transform: skewY(0deg); }
            .grid-container { flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 2rem; }
            .image-card { width: 200px; height: 200px; }
            .container { padding: 1rem; }
        }

        @keyframes slideInLeft {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateX(-100px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateX(0); }
        }

        @keyframes slideInUp {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(100px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        @keyframes fadeInScale {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: scale(0.8); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
        }


@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .image-card {
    width: 180px;
    height: 180px;
  }
}


    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Animated background elements -->
    <div class="wave-bg"></div>
    <div class="particle"></div>
    <div class="particle"></div>
    <div class="particle"></div>
    <div class="particle"></div>

    <div class="container">
        <!-- Header Section -->
        <header class="header">
            <div class="header-content">
                <h1 class="page-title">You-means </h1>
                <p class="subtitle" style="color: white;"> The irreplacable You</p>
            </div>
            <div class="header-decoration"></div>
        </header>

        <!-- Description Section -->
        <section class="description">
            <div class="description-content">
                <p class="description-text">
                    When i think about <span class="highlight">you</span> -(always thinks about you..),apart from the worries like Is she well?does she have food?Does she have a good day? i just smile..literally you make me happy girl even in my thoughts..<span class="highlight">I understand now my happiness is you..Just you..</span> my purpose in this life is to be with you..
                </p>
                
            </div>
        </section>

